<scriptment id="60000" point="hiring_3" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-08-28" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>The third wave of employees is here! Yuki looks at the candidates in the waiting area and grins.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Congratulations!</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">You are all among the third in Sega's equal opportunity employment effort.</line>
		<line id="3000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">It's great to see you've stepped up to the plate, Miss &#x2014; uh &#x2014;</line>
		<line id="4000" speaker="ayane" voicelang="ja">Dreyfus.</line>
		<line id="5000" speaker="ayane" voicelang="ja">Ayane Dreyfus.</line>
		<narration>A single strand of blonde protrudes from Ayane's head. She presses it down. She looks at the torus-smooth golden ring on Yuki's finger.</narration>
		<line id="6000" speaker="ayane" voicelang="ja">So I heard you got married, Mademoiselle.</line>
		<narration>Ayane winks.</narration>
		<line id="7000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Yeah, and I'm the cat.</line>
		<line id="8000" speaker="ayane" voicelang="ja">Oh my &#x2014; a bottom?</line>
		<narration>Yuki sighs.</narration>
		<line id="9000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">I guess so&#x2014;</line>
		<narration>Game Designer John Smith clears his throat.</narration>
		<line id="10000" speaker="john" voicelang="en">Ladies, this isn't too professional.</line>
		<line id="11000" speaker="john" voicelang="en">How about we get to the interview?</line>
		<narration>Computer Animator Ayane Dreyfus jumps.</narration>
		<line id="11100" speaker="ayane" voicelang="en">Oops, my apologies.</line>
		<line id="12000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="en">Of course, sir!</line>
		<narration>Yuki conducts the interview.</narration>
	</part>
</scriptment>